\emph default
 EoM, we have trivially non-interacting term 
\begin_inset Formula $-[\rho_{\text{eh}}\cdot h^{*}]|_{ab}-[h\cdot\rho_{\text{eh}}]|_{ab}$
\end_inset

.
 For the interaction terms we perform instead the mean-field decoupling
 of 
\begin_inset Formula $\langle c_{\alpha}^{\dagger}c_{\beta}c_{\gamma}c_{a}\rangle$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\langle c_{b}c_{\alpha}^{\dagger}c_{\beta}c_{\gamma}\rangle$
\end_inset

, we obtain
